long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Ace Stream ID Manager is a Chrome extension that makes it easy to open Ace Stream IDs with just a few clicks. It also allows you to keep track of your recently opened IDs, save IDs for later and search for specific IDs quickly. (Acestream IDs not provided).

Key features:

• Quick Ace Stream ID Opening:
Enter the Ace Stream ID in the provided input field, and with a simple click, the extension will open the Ace Stream content for you.

• Recent IDs Opened:
Keep track of your recently opened Ace Stream IDs, making it easy to revisit your favorite streams or quickly access previously viewed content.

• Save IDs for Later:
Save Ace Stream IDs for future use. The extension provides a list where you can save and manage your frequently used IDs, eliminating the need to enter them repeatedly.

• Search Functionality:
Find specific Ace Stream IDs quickly using the search bar. Simply type in the relevant keywords, and the extension will filter and display the matching IDs.

• Import & Export IDs:
Easily import or export your saved Ace Stream IDs for backup, sharing, or use across different devices.

Download Ace Stream ID Manager Chrome extension now and enhance your acestream experience. Quickly access football, sports, and other live streams while easily managing your favorite IDs.
